rformance.&lt;br&gt;• Diagnose and resolve performance and scalability issues.&lt;br&gt;• Collaborate with SRE teams to properly size infrastructure.&lt;br&gt;• Manage application and system configurations to ensure consistency and reproducibility (Desirable).&lt;br&gt;• Use tools like CloudFormation and Terraform to manage IAC (Desirable AWS).&lt;br&gt;• Automate the creation and configuration of infrastructure environments (Desirable).&lt;br&gt;• Promote an autonomous work culture by encouraging self-management, accountability, and proactive&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;problem-solving among team members.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
